# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Public (publishable) keys — safe to expose in the browser.
# These are auto-managed by Lovable Cloud; do NOT edit .env manually.
# This file is a TEMPLATE only. Copy to .env locally if self-hosting.
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
VITE_SUPABASE_PROJECT_ID="your-project-id"
VITE_SUPABASE_PUBLISHABLE_KEY="your-publishable-anon-key"
VITE_SUPABASE_URL="https://your-project-id.supabase.co"

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# PRIVATE keys — NEVER put these in .env or any VITE_* variable.
# Vite bundles every VITE_* variable into the client JS, exposing it.
# Store private keys as Edge Function secrets in Lovable Cloud
# (Cloud → Secrets) and access them via Deno.env.get("KEY_NAME").
#
# Currently stored as Edge Function secrets (server-side only):
#   - API_FOOTBALL_KEY        (api-football.com private key)
#   - SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY (auto-injected)
#   - SUPABASE_URL              (auto-injected)
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
